attributionInfo.brokerName: CJL Rentals & Property Management Co., Inc.
CJL Rentals & Property Management Co., Inc.

description: Great South Boston location just a short block to the Red Line, in the area seeing a great transformation! Not your typical garden level one-bedroom as the ceiling height makes a difference. This spacious condominium in a 4-unit building, features 10+ foot ceilings, large windows, stainless and granite kitchen with travertine backsplash, and updated bath. A bonus room off the kitchen is perfect for a dining area or an office. Enjoy late morning to an early afternoon sun, or grill yourself dinner, on an exclusive-use patio outside of your private entrance. There is also deeded storage, built-in shelving, and free washer/dryer in the common building area. Ideal location for commuters: in addition to proximity to the T, there is easy access to I-93. Enjoy everything the neighborhood has to offer with Carson Beach just a half-mile away, the first phase of the new Washington Village development completed, and South Bay and Southie bars/restaurants all close-by. Pet-friendly association.
